       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
           PROGRAM-ID. CALCUL-SALAIRE.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
        01 WS-EMPLOYEE-ID PIC 9(5).
        01 WS-EMPLOYEE-NAME PIC X(50).
        01 WS-SALARY-BASE PIC 9(7)V99.
        01 WS-BONUS PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.
        01 WS-TAX-RATE PIC 9V999 VALUE 0.22.
        01 WS-NET-SALARY PIC 9(7)V99.
        01 WS-GROSS-SALARY PIC 9(7)V99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           ACCEPT WS-EMPLOYEE-ID.
           PERFORM GET-EMPLOYEE-DATA.
           PERFORM CALCULATE-GROSS.
           PERFORM CALCULATE-NET.
           PERFORM DISPLAY-PAYSLIP.
           STOP RUN.

       GET-EMPLOYEE-DATA.
           MOVE "Jean Dupont" TO WS-EMPLOYEE-NAME.
           MOVE 3000.00 TO WS-SALARY-BASE.
           MOVE 500.00 TO WS-BONUS.

       CALCULATE-GROSS.
           COMPUTE WS-GROSS-SALARY = WS-SALARY-BASE + WS-BONUS.

       CALCULATE-NET.
           COMPUTE WS-NET-SALARY = WS-GROSS-SALARY * (1 - WS-TAX-RATE).

       DISPLAY-PAYSLIP.
           DISPLAY "Employee: " WS-EMPLOYEE-NAME.
           DISPLAY "Gross: " WS-GROSS-SALARY.
           DISPLAY "Net: " WS-NET-SALARY.
